Math¶

Note that backslashes need to be escaped!

If the math isn't rendered directly, refresh using Shift + F5 or Ctrl + Shift + R (in most browsers).

Inline: \(\alpha\)

Block:

\[\sum_{i = 1}^n w_i x_i\]
Inline: :math:`\alpha`

Block:

.. math::

    \sum_{i = 1}^n w_i x_i
